column16: Alex Rios pops out to second baseman Jemile Weeks in foul territory.
A.  J.   Pierzynski singles on a ground ball to second baseman Jemile Weeks.    Gordon Beckham scores.    Alejandro De Aza to 3rd.    Alexei Ramirez to 2nd.
Paul Konerko lines out to shortstop Cliff Pennington.
Jamey Carroll grounds out, second baseman Howard Kendrick to first baseman Albert Pujols.
Luke Hughes singles on a line drive to left fielder Vernon Wells.    Danny Valencia scores.
Ben Revere grounds out, second baseman Howard Kendrick to first baseman Albert Pujols.    Danny Valencia to 3rd.
Danny Valencia doubles (1) on a ground ball to left fielder Vernon Wells.    Josh Willingham scores.
Josh Willingham singles on a line drive to shortstop Maicer Izturis, deflected by third baseman Alberto Callaspo.
Justin Morneau homers (1) on a fly ball to right field.    Joe Mauer scores.
Joe Mauer singles on a line drive to right fielder Torii Hunter.
Eric Hosmer grounds out, second baseman Maicer Izturis to first baseman Albert Pujols.
Lorenzo Cain flies out to right fielder Torii Hunter.
